  marked stable on sparc - we shouldn't have -r1 laying around

  28 Dec 2003; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> fileutils-4.1.11-r2.ebuild:
  Move to mips stable (~mips -> mips)

  14 Dec 2003; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> fileutils-4.1.11-r2.ebuild:
  Marked stable on hppa.

  01 Oct 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> fileutils-4.1.11-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha to handle the coreutils changeover (see bug 30032)

